name: PHVS_MedicationDrugClass_HITSP
title: Medication Drug Class Value Set
description: This identifies the pharmacological drug class, such as Cephalosporins. Shall contain a value descending from the NDF-RT concept types of “Mechanism of Action - N0000000223”, “Physiologic Effect - N0000009802” or “Chemical Structure - N0000000002”`. NUI will be used as the concept code.
